need your compiler flags to contain:

	-F%p/lib/qt515-%type_pkg[qt]/lib

	or this:

	-I%p/lib/qt515-%type_pkg[qt]/include

...and your linker flags to contain:

	-F%p/lib/qt515-%type_pkg[qt]/lib

